<div id="review_226654672" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/226654672" />
    <a title="Sassafrass" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3275875-sassafrass"><img alt="Sassafrass" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1615648820p2/3275875.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/226654672?book_show_action=true">Oct 23, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sassafrass" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sassafrass" href="/user/show/3275875-sassafrass">Sassafrass</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9781612130491" href="/book/show/12189503-slave">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Sassafrass by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/3059210-debbie">Debbie </a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3275875-sassafrass?shelf=bdsm">bdsm</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3275875-sassafrass?shelf=z-2012">z-2012</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3275875-sassafrass?shelf=z-challenge-books-2012">z-challenge-books-2012</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3275875-sassafrass?shelf=z-src-sum12">z-src-sum12</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer226654672" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6101081485633108761">It&apos;s so hard to rate this book, but I went with 4.5 stars in the end.<br/><br/>I absolutely devoured this book, I will most likely read it again at some point. It was much different than I thought it would be. I had no idea how emotionally connected I would be to Brianna and Stephan. The horrors that Anna suffered at the hands of her forced Master were horrible, and we just got a small glimpse of them.<br/><br/>I was sad that the book ended where it did. I understand that it&apos;s part of a series but I would have like</span>
  <span id="freeText6101081485633108761" style="display:none">It's so hard to rate this book, but I went with 4.5 stars in the end.<br /><br />I absolutely devoured this book, I will most likely read it again at some point. It was much different than I thought it would be. I had no idea how emotionally connected I would be to Brianna and Stephan. The horrors that Anna suffered at the hands of her forced Master were horrible, and we just got a small glimpse of them.<br /><br />I was sad that the book ended where it did. I understand that it's part of a series but I would have liked a little more resolution to the story before it ended.<br /><br />I will say that I liked the shifting points of view in the story. Whenever there's a book that it's the first person, I'm always wondering how the other person sees things, so this way I got that in the one story.<br /><br />I'm on to the next story now. I've got an ARC from NetGalley, so I have to start it. There's no way that I can stop now. I need to...no HAVE to know what happens next.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6101081485633108761" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
